name: A summer day in the corn field

metadata.name: A summer day in the corn field.
metadata.description:
A summer day in the corn field

Olga couldn't understand why I kept running into the field to see if the sun was good.

When the time came, it had to be done quickly. Luckily it was a warm evening in Germany and it was no problem for Olga to walk around without clothes.

Created by Kostas Giannopoulos Photography August 2022
